BODY:
安裝與設定APC<br />-----------<br />linux:<br />可至<a href="http://pecl.php.net/package/APC">PECL下載APC</a><br /><br />下載APC後<br /><br /># tar xvzf APC-<st1:chsdate w:st="on" year="1899" month="12" day="30" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False">2.0.3</st1:chsdate>.tgz 解壓縮<br /># cd APC-<st1:chsdate w:st="on" year="1899" month="12" day="30" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False">2.0.3<br /></st1:chsdate># /usr/bin/phpize<br /># ./configure --enable-apc<br /># make<br /># make install <br /><br />windows:<br />可在<a href="http://pecl4win.php.net/list.php">PECL4Win下載編譯好的dll</a><br />請選擇適當版本自行丟到php include目錄中<br />----------<br /><br />接著更改php.ini設定<br /><br />貼上<br />linux:<br />extension = apc.so<br /><br />win:<br />extension = apc.dll<br /><br />apc.shm_segments=1<br />apc.optimization=0<br />apc.shm_size=128<br />apc.ttl=7200<br />apc.user_ttl=7200<br />apc.num_files_hint=1024<br />apc.mmap_file_mask=/tmp/apc.XXXXXX<br />apc.enable_cli=1<br />apc.rfc1867 = on<br /><br />重開apache2ctl graceful後，就安裝好了。<br />可至phpinfo.php檢查是否有正確啟動<br />或用壓縮檔中的apc.php查看apc資訊<!-- more -->
