<p>Awesome responsive bike. What can I say, its a Pro-Level frame. I like solid responsive bikes and was looking for a quick bike, but one that could also absorb some of road vibrations. This bike has exceeded all my expectations. It was a grat purchase.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>總之，最後決定購買啦。<br><br>整套傳動變速和輪組應該都可以轉上去，除了中變原本是28.6環抱沒法用。<br>座管不合，需要買新的。<br>車架則是有附龍頭把手。<br><br>原本的車架換下後，把手邊備料整一整，應該會組台旅行車吧。<br>這台GT鋼管原本就是旅行車式樣。我還你原形～<br><br>逛拍賣逛一逛，看到一張很便宜的座墊。<br><a href="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed017afd5.jpg"><img style="border: 0px none ;" src="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed0262d9a.jpg" "IMG_1821" border="0" width="260" height="200"></a> <br>雖然看外型就知道是velo代工的。<br>不過顏色實在是有夠搭這隻車架。<br>便宜的價格買來試坐看看都划算。<br><br>心中盤算，車架黑色，座墊白色。<br>若手把帶也纏白色應該效果會不錯。<br><br>於是下班就跑去附近的RST看手把帶。<br>RST跟鐵馬賽克不一樣，手把帶的種類不多。<br>白色的只有velo的小花手把帶。<br>不過滿好看，又便宜，買來試試看吧。<br><br>在RST也看到jagwire的白色線組。<br>配備非常齊全，會讓人忍不住想：「高級車就是要配這種線組啊」<br>於是又敗下去了...。<br><a href="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed036875f.jpg"><img style="border: 0px none ;" src="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed0451e64.jpg" "IMG_1818" border="0" width="260" height="200"></a> <br><a href="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed0540b0e.jpg"><img style="border: 0px none ;" src="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed0641315.jpg" "IMG_1819" border="0" width="260" height="200"></a> <br><br>最後順手帶了一隻拆外掛BB的工具，<br>這樣就不用去車店借了。<br>說實在，回台北後我還不知道要去哪借呢。<br><br>Parktool~價格不菲啊。<br><a href="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed073c951.jpg"><img style="border: 0px none ;" src="http://p4.p.pixnet.net/albums/userpics/4/5/761745/48bfed0846fc0.jpg" "IMG_1820" border="0" width="260" height="200"></a> <br><br>期待明天帶車架、座管和中變回來，就可以開工啦。</p>
